31 March 2017 Members of the media covering the official memorial service of the late Mr Ahmed “Kathy” Kathrada are advised that there is an accreditation process that they need to follow. To apply for accreditation kindly complete an online registration form by following the link: https://www.gcis.gov.za/content/media-registration.  It is important that you verify your details when completing the form. Media are advised to take note of the following details: The memorial service will take place as follows: Date:              Saturday, 01 April 2017 Time:             11h00 Venue:           University of Johannesburg Soweto Campus, Soweto For further information on accreditation contact: Ishmael Selemale on 061 790 5114. Issued by Government Communication and Information System 